==Serbian==
===Greeting===
'''Vaistinu se rodi'''
#[[Merry Christmas]] (''greeting'')
#(''literally''): [[verily|Verily]], [[Jesus|he]] [[has]] [[been]] [[born]].
*:''Note:  This is only the '''reply''' part of the greeting.  The ''greeting'' part preceding the reply is [[Hristos se rodi#Serbian|Hristos se rodi]].''
